name: Rite Of Passage
Lore: 'There are many different paths to becoming a Jedi, each with its own risks and consequences. A student must choose wisely.',
Text: 'At the beginning of opponent''s move phase, target an opponent''s character alone at a mobile site and select an adjacent site. Opponent must choose to move target there for free (target cannot move for remainder of turn), lose target or lose 2 Force.',
